Wano arc face 1:
   The wano arc consist of two faces in which the first face consists of the planing and training session for the straw hat pirates were the minks tribe ,
ninjas and the wano people plan for the battle at onigashima.
  During the face one luffy and eustas kid are kept as slaves because they are captured by kaido .
in the begining of this arc luffy,brook,sanji,chopper,nami and carrot manage to escape from the whole cake island from bigmom with the hep of jinbe ,
same time in wano kin gave different roles for the other straw hat members like zoro as a common ronin , ussop as a toad oil seller ,sanji as a soba cook,
robin as a dancer, franky as a carpenter to steel onigashima palace plan .
   but zoro got caught at the begining itself for another ones crime and sentenced to death but zoro escaped 
after that he met luffy in wano unexpectedly . after that luffy got to meet kaido and fight him with his full power in gear 4 but its not enough literaly
thats when luffy got captured by kaido and his allies.
kaido left luffy as a slave in a prison.
the other members stayed calm and waited for the plan to be well executed , they know that luffy will be allright .
after that luffy got the controll of the prison by his power and trained in there until they get to onigashima .
also with help of franky they made enough ships to travel .
after that odens brother got killed by orochi because the plan got leaked , same time tama the daughter of odens brother was also a enemy for orochi 
who was nearly got to be killed by orochi but at that time zoro and sanji didnt just stand and watch they becomed raged and started to fight against orochi to save
tama and odens daughter hiyori zoro exchanged his sword for enma because the sword he kept also belongs to a legendary swords man from wano .
after that they made a new plan and new departure port to battle in onigashima .
this is were the face 1 of wano ends ................


